defaultWe expect the implementation rules associated with the ecological focus areas measure to respect the European Council declaration of the 8 February 2013:  
default“The requirement to have an ecological focus area (EFA) on each agricultural holding will be implemented in ways that do not require the land in question to be taken out of production and that avoids unjustified losses in the income of farmers”.
